posting_body: ['Property Address', '1299 Grand Ave - 201 | St. Paul, MN 55105', 'Available: 10/01/2022', 'Offered By', 'At Home Apartments', 'Description', 'Sun-Drenched, Front Corner One Bedroom Overlooking Grand Ave at The Grand Heritage Apartments', 'This apartment features shiny hardwood floors, updated windows and light fixtures throughout,original 1920s built ins in the kitchen, generous closet space and a huge bedroom.', 'Grand Heritage residents have access to the rental office, an upscale grocery store, our exclusive fitness center and clubhouse--all less than one block away!', 'With a top-notch location along the tree-lined street of Grand Avenue, the Grand Heritage Apartments boasts of historical charm combined with gorgeous updates making modern living more convenient.', "Just one block south of Summit Avenue and next door to the famous Kowalski's Market, you are sure to find yourself in the best of Grand Avenue living.", 'Call us at', 'show contact info', 'or visit us at <URL> for more information and tour options.', 'Photos are a representation of the property and may not be of the exact apartment.', '**$150 Administration Fee added to lease.', 'Final price subject to change pending walk-through inspection.', 'Pet fees/restrictions may apply.', 'Please inquire about your specific pet.', '**', 'Amenities', 'Heat Paid', 'Water Paid', 'Trash/Recycling Paid', 'Secured Entry', 'Laundry On-Site', 'On Bus Route', 'Fitness Center and Clubhouse Across the Street', '24-Hour Emergency Maintenance', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 1BD/1.0BA', 'Square Feet: 800', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $1,076.00', 'Available: 10/01/2022', 'Application Fee: $55.00', 'Security Deposit: $600.00', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats allowed', 'Dogs not allowed']
